WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.500
Four billion, one hundred and eleven million dollars.

00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:09.000
That's what the Haitian diaspora sent home in a single year — 2024.

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:13.500
The number is true. But today, I'll use it to tell you three lies.

00:00:13.500 --> 00:00:17.000
Three lies you won't even notice.

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:21.500
Welcome to Lojik360 — data, logic, decisions.

00:00:21.500 --> 00:00:27.000
In this lesson, you'll learn how to stop letting numbers fool you.
